=====================================================

Logical Operators

Assignment operator: =
Arithmetic: +, -, *, /, %
Relational: >, =, <, <=, >=, !=

Logical: &&, || !

Logical AND &&

true && true ---> TRUE
true && false ---> FALSE
false && true ---> FALSE
false && false ---> FALSE


Logical OR

true || true --->TRUE
true || false ---> TRUE
false || true ---> TRUE
false || false ---> FALSE

Logical !

true || true --->
true || false ---> 
false || true ---> 
false || false ---> 






